  "tool": "adjust_inventory",
  "arguments": {
    "item_id": "SKU-442",
    "quantity": 5,
    "reason": "return"
  }
}
```

The correction removes the negative sign from the quantity parameter, changing it from `-5` to `5`, which satisfies the requirement that quantity must be a positive integer.

